{"title":"狼  是谁绞杀人民的和平","authors":["柯岗"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":8,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁绞杀人民的和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沁河边上的麦苗嫩绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沁河边上的菜花金黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝妞——沁河边上的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她打扮的就像花朵样："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉红裤子，浅蓝衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提着小竹篮，伴着白发娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们要去探亲戚啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去给外婆上坟烧香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们向东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那开满黄花的地边走过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守卫边村的民兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在唱着毛主席的歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那蓝妞还低声的和。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是她们只穿过一块麦田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只翻过一座沙岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只走了一里多路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到叶岭村西就碰见了“狼”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“狼”，脖上挂着“中央牌”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“狼”，说着中国话，拿着美国枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“狼”，瞪着红眼珠把蓝妞上下打量："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“站住，八路探子，那里去”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老总：去给她外婆烧纸哩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说和平啦，东西通行”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哼！和平？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他和，咱可不和，…………”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“狼”，拉着蓝妞进柳林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝妞哭着就地滚，…………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是到黄昏后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝妞和她娘都又转来了，她们顺着黄花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地边走回自己的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可惜蓝妞变啦："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的头发揉乱啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的衣衫扯烂啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她光哭不说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不到天明她就上吊啦！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九四六，五月）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}